										at the new location to get set up before your appointment,
										enter the time in minutes here. And the Outbound Buffer
										Minutes: When you travel between locations and want to have
										some time when leaving this location to get your bags packed
										and get in your car, enter the time in minutes here set to
										the amount of time.
